This paper focuses on the task of grounding referring expressions in images, which is a problem in computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of scene graphs, which are a common tool in computer vision research. This suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-categories of cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
